trans-unit.source: Returns an array of all of the color/alpha components in normalized form, given a pixel in this ColorModel. The pixel value is specified by an array of data elements of type transferType passed in as an object reference. If pixel is not a primitive array of type transferType, a ClassCastException is thrown. An ArrayIndexOutOfBoundsException is thrown if pixel is not large enough to hold a pixel value for this ColorModel. Normalized components are float values between a per component minimum and maximum specified by the ColorSpace object for this ColorModel. If the normComponents array is null, a new array will be allocated. The normComponents array will be returned. Color/alpha components are stored in the normComponents array starting at normOffset (even if the array is allocated by this method). An ArrayIndexOutOfBoundsException is thrown if the normComponents array is not null and is not large enough to hold all the color and alpha components (starting at normOffset).
trans-unit.target: 给定此 ColorModel 中的一个像素，以归一化形式返回所有颜色/ alpha分量的数组。像素值由作为对象引用传入的类型为transferType的数据元素数组指定。如果pixel不是transferType类型的原始数组，则抛出 ClassCastException 。一个 ArrayIndexOutOfBoundsException 异常是否抛出 pixel 不够大，不能保存此像素值 ColorModel 。规范化的组件是此 ColorModel 的 ColorSpace 对象指定的每个组件的最小值与最大值之间的浮点值。如果 normComponents 数组为 null ，将分配一个新数组。该 normComponents 的数组将被返回。颜色/ alpha分量存储中 normComponents 数组以 normOffset 开头（即使该阵列由这种方法分配的）。一个 ArrayIndexOutOfBoundsException 异常如果被抛出 normComponents 数组不 null 和不够大以容纳所有的颜色和alpha分量（在开始 normOffset 开头）。

trans-unit.source: Returns an array of all of the color/alpha components in normalized form, given a pixel in this ColorModel. The pixel value is specified by an array of data elements of type transferType passed in as an object reference. If pixel is not a primitive array of type transferType, a ClassCastException is thrown. An ArrayIndexOutOfBoundsException is thrown if pixel is not large enough to hold a pixel value for this ColorModel. Normalized components are float values between a per component minimum and maximum specified by the ColorSpace object for this ColorModel. If the normComponents array is null, a new array will be allocated. The normComponents array will be returned. Color/alpha components are stored in the normComponents array starting at normOffset (even if the array is allocated by this method). An ArrayIndexOutOfBoundsException is thrown if the normComponents array is not null and is not large enough to hold all the color and alpha components (starting at normOffset). Since ColorModel is an abstract class, any instance is an instance of a subclass. The default implementation of this method in this abstract class first retrieves color and alpha components in the unnormalized form using getComponents(Object, int[], int) and then calls getNormalizedComponents(int[], int, float[], int). Subclasses which may have instances which do not support the unnormalized form must override this method.
trans-unit.target: 给定此 ColorModel 中的一个像素，以归一化形式返回所有颜色/ alpha分量的数组。像素值由作为对象引用传入的类型为transferType的数据元素数组指定。如果pixel不是transferType类型的原始数组，则抛出 ClassCastException 。一个 ArrayIndexOutOfBoundsException 异常是否抛出 pixel 不够大，不能保存此像素值 ColorModel 。规范化的组件是此 ColorModel 的 ColorSpace 对象指定的每个组件的最小值与最大值之间的浮点值。如果 normComponents 数组为 null ，将分配一个新数组。该 normComponents 的数组将被返回。颜色/ alpha分量存储中 normComponents 数组以 normOffset 开头（即使该阵列由这种方法分配的）。一个 ArrayIndexOutOfBoundsException 异常如果被抛出 normComponents 数组不 null 和不够大以容纳所有的颜色和alpha分量（在开始 normOffset 开头）。由于 ColorModel 是抽象类，因此任何实例都是子类的实例。此抽象类中此方法的默认实现首先使用以下方法以非规范化形式检索颜色和alpha分量： getComponents(Object, int[], int) ，然后调用 getNormalizedComponents(int[], int, float[], int) 。可能具有不支持非标准化形式的实例的子类必须重写此方法。

trans-unit.source: Returns an array of all of the color/alpha components in normalized form, given an unnormalized component array.
trans-unit.target: 给定一个未归一化的分量数组,返回一个归一化形式的所有颜色/alpha分量的数组。

trans-unit.source: Returns an array of all of the color/alpha components in normalized form, given an unnormalized component array. Unnormalized components are unsigned integral values between 0 and 2n - 1, where n is the number of bits for a particular component. Normalized components are float values between a per component minimum and maximum specified by the ColorSpace object for this ColorModel. An IllegalArgumentException will be thrown if color component values for this ColorModel are not conveniently representable in the unnormalized form. If the normComponents array is null, a new array will be allocated. The normComponents array will be returned. Color/alpha components are stored in the normComponents array starting at normOffset (even if the array is allocated by this method). An ArrayIndexOutOfBoundsException is thrown if the normComponents array is not null and is not large enough to hold all the color and alpha components (starting at normOffset). An IllegalArgumentException is thrown if the components array is not large enough to hold all the color and alpha components starting at offset.
trans-unit.target: 给定一个未归一化的分量数组，以归一化形式返回所有颜色/ alpha分量的数组。未归一化的分量是介于0到2 n -1之间的无符号整数值，其中n是特定分量的位数。规范化的组件是此 ColorModel 的 ColorSpace 对象指定的每个组件的最小值与最大值之间的浮点值。一个 IllegalArgumentException 如果这种颜色成分值会被抛出 ColorModel 不便于用非标准化形式表示。如果 normComponents 数组为 null ，则将分配一个新数组。该 normComponents 的数组将被返回。颜色/ alpha分量存储中 normComponents 数组以 normOffset 开头（即使该阵列由这种方法分配的）。一个 ArrayIndexOutOfBoundsException 异常如果被抛出 normComponents 数组不 null 和不够大以容纳所有的颜色和alpha分量（在开始 normOffset 开头）。一个 IllegalArgumentException 如果抛出 components 阵列并不大到足以容纳所有的颜色和alpha分量开始 offset 。

trans-unit.source: Returns an array of arrays of Annotations that represent the annotations on the formal parameters, in declaration order, of the Executable represented by this object. Synthetic and mandated parameters (see explanation below), such as the outer "this" parameter to an inner class constructor will be represented in the returned array. If the executable has no parameters (meaning no formal, no synthetic, and no mandated parameters), a zero-length array will be returned. If the Executable has one or more parameters, a nested array of length zero is returned for each parameter with no annotations. The annotation objects contained in the returned arrays are serializable. The caller of this method is free to modify the returned arrays; it will have no effect on the arrays returned to other callers. A compiler may add extra parameters that are implicitly declared in source ("mandated"), as well as parameters that are neither implicitly nor explicitly declared in source ("synthetic") to the parameter list for a method. See Parameter for more information.
trans-unit.target: 返回一个 Annotation 数组，该数组按声明顺序表示此对象表示的 Executable 的形式参数上的注释。综合和强制性参数（请参见下面的说明），例如内部类构造函数的外部“ this”参数将在返回的数组中表示。如果可执行文件没有参数（意味着没有形式参数，合成参数和强制参数），则将返回零长度数组。如果 Executable 具有一个或多个参数，则对每个没有注释的参数返回长度为零的嵌套数组。返回数组中包含的注释对象是可序列化的。此方法的调用者可以自由修改返回的数组；它对返回给其他调用方的数组没有影响。编译器可能会在方法的参数列表中添加在源中隐式声明的额外参数（“强制”），以及在源中“隐式”声明既未隐式声明也未添加参数（“合成”）。有关更多信息，请参见 Parameter 。

trans-unit.source: Returns an array of glyph positions for the specified glyphs. This method is used for convenience and performance when processing glyph positions. If no array is passed in, a new array is created. Even numbered array entries beginning with position zero are the X coordinates of the glyph numbered beginGlyphIndex + position/2. Odd numbered array entries beginning with position one are the Y coordinates of the glyph numbered beginGlyphIndex + (position-1)/2. If beginGlyphIndex equals the number of glyphs in this GlyphVector, this method gets the position after the last glyph and this position is used to define the advance of the entire GlyphVector.
trans-unit.target: 返回指定字形的字形位置数组。处理字形位置时，此方法用于方便性和性能。如果没有传递任何数组，则会创建一个新的数组。从位置零开始的偶数编号的数组条目是编号为 beginGlyphIndex + position/2 的字形的X坐标。从位置1开始的编号为奇数的数组条目是编号为 beginGlyphIndex + (position-1)/2 的字形的Y坐标。如果 beginGlyphIndex 等于此 GlyphVector 中的字形数量，则此方法获取最后一个字形之后的位置，并且此位置用于定义整个 GlyphVector 的前进。
